---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team - Inform Growth | AI-Native Revenue Operations"
  description="A systems architect and a sales closer. We build AI infrastructure that sales teams actually use - because we've been on both sides of broken RevOps."
>
  <!-- Section 1: The Origin -->
  <section class="origin-section section geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="origin-content fade-up">
        <h1>We've seen what happens when RevOps and AI are disconnected from real selling.</h1>
        <div class="origin-story">
          <p>
            Jaron built revenue systems for scaling companies - 400K+ records migrated, 7 CRMs consolidated, enterprise data architectures designed. He watched operators route around the very systems he built because they were designed without understanding how deals actually close.
          </p>
          <p>
            Joseph closed enterprise deals at Checkout.com - $900K contracts, 70% YoY growth. He watched RevOps consultants design processes that ignored how sales actually work. Then watched AI tools get deployed in silos - sales using ChatGPT, marketing with different tools, no one owning the outputs.
          </p>
          <p class="origin-conclusion">
            <strong>Inform Growth is their answer:</strong> AI-native revenue infrastructure designed by people who've had to sell with broken tools - and fix the systems that broke them. We bring our own AI layer. You keep the learnings. Context never resets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Founder Profiles -->
  <section class="profiles-section section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center fade-up">The Founders</h2>

      <div class="founders-grid fade-up">
        <!-- Jaron Sander -->
        <div class="founder-profile">
          <div class="founder-header">
            <div class="founder-avatar">
              <span>JS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-title">
              <h3>Jaron Sander</h3>
              <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder / Revenue Systems Architect</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="founder-bio">
            Builds the systems that make revenue predictable. Player-coach model - still in the code, still on client calls. Started as a one-person RevOps team and learned that the best systems are the ones operators actually use.
          </p>

          <div class="founder-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">400K+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Records Migrated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">75%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">CRM Cost Reduction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">40%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Churn Reduction</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-credentials">
            <h4>Credentials</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Led RevOps for 3x scaling SaaS companies</li>
              <li>Consolidated 7 CRMs into unified architecture</li>
              <li>Built custom integrations across HubSpot, Salesforce, and Segment</li>
              <li>Designed data architectures serving 3M+ contacts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-tools">
            <h4>Core Tools</h4>
            <p>HubSpot, Salesforce, Segment, Python, SQL, Make, n8n, Custom APIs</p>
          </div>

          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jaron-sander" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="founder-linkedin">
            Connect on LinkedIn →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Joseph Anthony -->
        <div class="founder-profile">
          <div class="founder-header">
            <div class="founder-avatar">
              <span>JA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-title">
              <h3>Joseph Anthony</h3>
              <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder / Enterprise Sales</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="founder-bio">
            Closes the deals that prove the systems work. Learned at Checkout.com and Ivey Business School that sales tools only matter if sellers can actually sell with them. The systems architect's built-in stress test.
          </p>

          <div class="founder-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">$900K</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Largest Deal Closed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">$2M</span>
              <span class="metric-label">New Business (4 mo)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">70%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Revenue Growth</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-credentials">
            <h4>Credentials</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Enterprise Account Executive at Checkout.com</li>
              <li>Ivey Business School (HBA)</li>
              <li>$110K non-dilutive funding secured</li>
              <li>Built outbound engines from zero pipeline</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-tools">
            <h4>Core Tools</h4>
            <p>HubSpot Sales Hub, Gong, Outreach, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, Notion</p>
          </div>

          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/josephanthony" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="founder-linkedin">
            Connect on LinkedIn →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Why We Work This Way -->
  <section class="why-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center fade-up">Why We Work This Way</h2>

      <div class="why-grid fade-up">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">1</div>
          <h3>The Problem We Kept Seeing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>RevOps is overloaded maintaining tools, not architecting for AI</li>
            <li>Sales, Marketing, CS all using different AI tools - no governance</li>
            <li>Consultants diagnose but don't fix; context gets lost in handoffs</li>
            <li>Every operator starts from zero - learnings don't compound</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">2</div>
          <h3>What We Built Instead</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>We bring our own AI layer - no 6-month vendor evaluations</li>
            <li>Zero-handoff model - one team from diagnosis to deployment</li>
            <li>Sales architect + systems architect on every engagement</li>
            <li>We scope, build, AND operate inside your stack</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">3</div>
          <h3>What It Means for You</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Unified AI layer across your revenue stack - shared context, not silos</li>
            <li>Output ships fast - we bring tooling, not RFP processes</li>
            <li>Your RevOps team gets back to strategy, not maintenance</li>
            <li>System learns from every deal - context never resets</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: CTA -->
  <section class="team-cta section geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content fade-up">
        <h2>Let's find what's leaking - and what fragmentation is costing you.</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">30 minutes. We map the fragmentation across your revenue stack. $100K+ in recovered pipeline or you don't pay.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book Your Deep-Scan</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Just want to talk first →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section 1: Origin */
  .origin-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
    padding: var(--space-section) 0;
  }

  .origin-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .origin-section h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .origin-story {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .origin-story p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .origin-conclusion {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.1);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--sky-blue);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
  }

  .origin-conclusion strong {
    color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  /* Section 2: Profiles */
  .profiles-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .founders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .founders-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .founder-profile {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    padding: var(--space-7);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .founder-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founder-avatar span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  .founder-title h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .founder-role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .metric {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .founder-credentials h4,
  .founder-tools h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .founder-credentials ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .founder-credentials li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .founder-credentials li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--emerald);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .founder-tools p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-linkedin {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .founder-linkedin:hover {
    color: var(--sky-blue-light);
  }

  /* Section 3: Why We Work This Way */
  .why-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
  }

  .why-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .why-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    padding: var(--space-7);
  }

  .why-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background-color: #E8F5D0;
    color: #2D5016;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .why-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .why-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .why-card li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .why-card li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Section 4: CTA */
  .team-cta {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  /* Scroll animations */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .fade-up.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Scroll-triggered fade-up animations
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const fadeElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, {
      threshold: 0.1,
      rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
    });

    fadeElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
